{"tid":1753973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍屍：區議會冇用，選到立法會先講","createTime":"2019-11-25T05:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T05:44:51.000Z","uid":20809,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0d6f3660e32b042ba7dc2209acf2860f8eaf3eaa","tid":1753973,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔撚洗自我安慰喇，依家就係贏撚到開巷，民意係晒呢邊，乜撚野選票64比，用埋d種票/鬼票/掌心雷同埋推d神智不清既廢老去，都係得4成，4成入面有幾多水份心照啦。<br />\n<br />\n真係迫不及待想去串鳩d黑警了<br />\n<br />\nbtw,果d先天下之憂而憂，後天下之樂而樂既人可唔可以收皮，贏都唔敢贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142d42571a5621ad59102f86845fd0edfd043449","tid":1753973,"uid":14912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"立法會無用, 選到人大先講"},{"pid":"48a5ba373acd3e34eede5bad509dba343fa047fa","tid":1753973,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e26104706fbeec5a892506f549c13b17f0b8028c","tid":1753973,"uid":20809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:26:37.000Z","msg":"營救poly手足行動第二波 1/20"},{"pid":"